# nightout-mobile + NightOut web

- **Mobile app**: this repository (`nightout-mobile`).
- **Web companion**: **`NightOut`** (typically `../NightOut` next to this repo).
- For product features that exist on both apps, **mirror behavior and data contracts** (e.g. DM message formats, venue share payloads, navigation back to the same conversation) unless the user asks for mobile-only or web-only work.
